                    Answers to Logikbots SQL Course at
                    https://www.logikbot.com/courses/the-fundamentals-of-transact-sql-for-machine-learning-engineers


Question 1 
Write a SELECT statement that lists the customers along with their ID numbers. Include the last names, first names, and company names.

Answer
SELECT 
	CustomerID,
	FirstName,
	LastName,
	CompanyName
FROM SalesLT.Customer


Question 2
Write a SELECT statement that lists the name, product number, and color of each product.

Answer
SELECT
	Name,
	ProductNumber,
	Color
FROM SalesLT.Product


Question 3
Write a SELECT statement that lists the customer ID numbers and sales order ID numbers from the SalesLT.SalesOrderHeader table

Answer
SELECT
	SalesOrderID,
	CustomerID
FROM SalesLT.SalesOrderHeader


Question 4
**** Need to use the AdventureWorks 2019 database
Write a query using a WHERE clause that displays all the employees listed in the HumanResources.
Employee table who have the job title Research and Development Engineer. 
Display the business entity ID number, the login ID, and the title for each one.

Answer
SELECT
	BusinessEntityID, 
	LoginID,
	JobTitle
FROM HumanResources.Employee
WHERE JobTitle = 'Research and Development Engineer'


